Contribution: Fast clustering scheme to form stable clusters
Problem: high mobility that results to limited time.


Algorithm

Environment: Road with mobile beacons that advertise their state.
Percepts: {hear({state: "3"})}
Actuators: [send({query_destination: <cluster-head>, query_message: ""})]

Data (Packets):
- Hello (6)
- Triggering (5)
- Initiating (5)
- Announce (3)
- ACK (3)
- ACK_CH ( 4 + cm_function([CMs])


